---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Investors | Fluidity Marine Seed Round">
  <main class="page">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="investor-hero animate-in">
      <div class="badge">
        <span class="badge-dot"></span>
        <span>Seed Round — Open on Wefunder</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="page-title">
        Join the <span class="electric-text">Seed Phase</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="page-subtitle">
        InnovativeDynamix is scaling the future of maritime technology. 
        Our ABLTV platform eliminates the mechanical rudder — an opportunity to participate 
        in a fundamental paradigm shift in marine propulsion.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Quick Stats -->
    <section class="stats-grid animate-in delay-1">
      <div class="stat-card glass-box">
        <span class="stat-card-label">Stage</span>
        <span class="stat-card-value">Seed (Open)</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card glass-box">
        <span class="stat-card-label">Platform</span>
        <span class="stat-card-value">Wefunder</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card glass-box">
        <span class="stat-card-label">Tech Moat</span>
        <span class="stat-card-value">ABLTV Patent-Pending</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card glass-box">
        <span class="stat-card-label">Propulsion Era</span>
        <span class="stat-card-value">Post-Appendage</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- The Investment Thesis -->
    <hr class="divider" />
    <section class="thesis-section animate-in delay-2">
      <h2 class="section-title">The Investment Thesis</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Why ABLTV represents a generational opportunity in marine technology.</p>

      <div class="thesis-grid">
        <div class="card thesis-card">
          <div class="thesis-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M16 8h-6a2 2 0 100 4h4a2 2 0 110 4H8"/><path d="M12 18V6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Massive TAM, Zero Competition</h3>
          <p>The global marine propulsion market is valued at $12B+ annually. No competitor offers a rudderless, software-defined thrust vectoring system. ABLTV is in a category of one.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card thesis-card">
          <div class="thesis-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>3D-Printable Moat</h3>
          <p>Our modular, 3D-printable architecture enables regional manufacturing without centralized shipyards. Lower CapEx to scale, faster deployment, and supply chain resilience.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card thesis-card">
          <div class="thesis-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>IP-Protected Infrastructure</h3>
          <p>Patent-pending ABLTV technology forms a defensible moat. The system is entirely software-controlled, creating opportunities for recurring revenue through digital fleet management and over-the-air updates.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card thesis-card">
          <div class="thesis-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 8h1a4 4 0 010 8h-1"/><path d="M2 8h16v9a4 4 0 01-4 4H6a4 4 0 01-4-4V8z"/><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="4"/><line x1="10" y1="1" x2="10" y2="4"/><line x1="14" y1="1" x2="14" y2="4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Regulatory Tailwinds</h3>
          <p>Global emissions regulations are phasing out internal combustion marine engines. Electric propulsion is the only compliant path forward, and ABLTV is the most advanced electric propulsion architecture in development.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Vision Brief -->
    <hr class="divider" />
    <section class="vision-section animate-in delay-3">
      <h2 class="section-title">Scaling the Maritime Operating System</h2>
      <p class="vision-text">
        Fluidity Marine is more than a propulsion company. We are building the modular IP core — 
        ABLTV — that will power a new generation of high-efficiency, low-maintenance vessels. 
        From commercial transit to aspirational lifestyle anchors like <strong>The Floating Bar</strong>, 
        our technology is the common denominator.
      </p>

      <div class="vision-stats">
        <div class="vision-stat">
          <span class="vision-stat-value">$12B+</span>
          <span class="vision-stat-label">Total Addressable Market</span>
        </div>
        <div class="vision-stat">
          <span class="vision-stat-value">60%</span>
          <span class="vision-stat-label">Fewer Failure Points</span>
        </div>
        <div class="vision-stat">
          <span class="vision-stat-value">100%</span>
          <span class="vision-stat-label">Electric Propulsion</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Milestones -->
    <hr class="divider" />
    <section class="milestones-section animate-in delay-3">
      <h2 class="section-title">Roadmap & Milestones</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Our path from laboratory to global infrastructure.</p>

      <div class="milestone-timeline">
        <div class="milestone completed">
          <div class="milestone-marker"></div>
          <div class="milestone-content">
            <span class="milestone-status">Completed</span>
            <h3>ABLTV Proof of Concept</h3>
            <p>Validated Active Boundary Layer Thrust Vectoring through fluid dynamic simulation and rapid prototyping.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="milestone active">
          <div class="milestone-marker"></div>
          <div class="milestone-content">
            <span class="milestone-status">Active</span>
            <h3>Seed Round & Web Presence</h3>
            <p>Open equity crowdfunding on Wefunder. Building the digital and physical infrastructure for scaled production.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="milestone">
          <div class="milestone-marker"></div>
          <div class="milestone-content">
            <span class="milestone-status">Q3 2026</span>
            <h3>Technical Whitepaper Release</h3>
            <p>Comprehensive publication of ABLTV engineering specifications, simulation results, and performance data.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="milestone">
          <div class="milestone-marker"></div>
          <div class="milestone-content">
            <span class="milestone-status">Q4 2026</span>
            <h3>First Prototype Vessel</h3>
            <p>Full-scale ABLTV integration into a demonstrator vessel for sea trials and validation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="milestone">
          <div class="milestone-marker"></div>
          <div class="milestone-content">
            <span class="milestone-status">2027</span>
            <h3>Commercial Deployment</h3>
            <p>First commercial ABLTV units deployed. Regional manufacturing hubs operational.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Offering Details -->
    <hr class="divider" />
    <section class="offering-section animate-in delay-3">
      <h2 class="section-title">Offering Details</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Terms and structure of the Fluidity Marine seed round.</p>

      <div class="glass-box offering-card">
        <div class="offering-grid">
          <div class="offering-item">
            <span class="offering-label">Issuer</span>
            <span class="offering-value">Fluidity Marine Inc. (Delaware C-Corp)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="offering-item">
            <span class="offering-label">Founded</span>
            <span class="offering-value">2023</span>
          </div>
          <div class="offering-item">
            <span class="offering-label">Pre-money Valuation</span>
            <span class="offering-value">$5,000,000</span>
          </div>
          <div class="offering-item">
            <span class="offering-label">Security Type</span>
            <span class="offering-value">Series Seed Preferred Stock (or SAFEs via Wefunder)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="offering-item">
            <span class="offering-label">Minimum Investment</span>
            <span class="offering-value">$50,000 private / No minimum via Wefunder</span>
          </div>
          <div class="offering-item">
            <span class="offering-label">Investor Rights</span>
            <span class="offering-value">Information rights, pro-rata participation, voting</span>
          </div>
          <div class="offering-item">
            <span class="offering-label">Target</span>
            <span class="offering-value">$5M startup capital</span>
          </div>
          <div class="offering-item">
            <span class="offering-label">Revenue</span>
            <span class="offering-value">Projected $10M sales/pre-orders in year 2</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Use of Funds -->
    <hr class="divider" />
    <section class="funds-section animate-in delay-3">
      <h2 class="section-title">Use of Funds</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">How the $5M seed capital will be deployed to scale ABLTV from prototype to global infrastructure.</p>

      <div class="funds-grid">
        <div class="card funds-card">
          <div class="funds-header">
            <div class="funds-bar bar-rd" style="width: 30%"></div>
            <span class="funds-pct">30%</span>
          </div>
          <h3>R&amp;D and Prototyping</h3>
          <p>Full-scale prototype development, sea trials, iterative engineering, and advanced fluid dynamic simulation to refine ABLTV performance across vessel classes.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card funds-card">
          <div class="funds-header">
            <div class="funds-bar bar-mkt" style="width: 25%"></div>
            <span class="funds-pct">25%</span>
          </div>
          <h3>Marketing &amp; Community Building</h3>
          <p>Brand development, digital presence, Wefunder campaign amplification, content creation, and community engagement to build a global movement around rudderless propulsion.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card funds-card">
          <div class="funds-header">
            <div class="funds-bar bar-ops" style="width: 20%"></div>
            <span class="funds-pct">20%</span>
          </div>
          <h3>Operations &amp; Staffing</h3>
          <p>Key engineering hires, operations team, supply chain management, and administrative infrastructure to support rapid scaling from lab to commercial deployment.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card funds-card">
          <div class="funds-header">
            <div class="funds-bar bar-legal" style="width: 10%"></div>
            <span class="funds-pct">10%</span>
          </div>
          <h3>Legal &amp; Compliance</h3>
          <p>Patent prosecution and IP protection, regulatory compliance, securities law counsel, and corporate governance for a growing Delaware C-Corp.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card funds-card">
          <div class="funds-header">
            <div class="funds-bar bar-wc" style="width: 15%"></div>
            <span class="funds-pct">15%</span>
          </div>
          <h3>Working Capital</h3>
          <p>Operating runway, inventory buffer, contingency reserves, and financial flexibility to navigate the journey from seed to revenue generation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Market Size -->
    <hr class="divider" />
    <section class="market-section animate-in delay-3">
      <h2 class="section-title">Market Size</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">A vast and underserved global opportunity in marine propulsion.</p>

      <div class="market-stats">
        <div class="market-stat glass-box">
          <span class="market-stat-value">$170B+</span>
          <span class="market-stat-label">Global Marine Vessel Market</span>
          <p class="market-stat-desc">The worldwide marine vessel market spans commercial shipping, defense, recreational boating, and maritime infrastructure — representing a multi-trillion-dollar installed base in need of modernisation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="market-stat glass-box">
          <span class="market-stat-value">$12B+</span>
          <span class="market-stat-label">Marine Propulsion Market (Annual)</span>
          <p class="market-stat-desc">Global spend on marine engines, propulsion systems, and related components exceeds $12 billion per year — and the transition to electric is just beginning.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="market-channels">
        <h3>Go-to-Market Channels</h3>
        <div class="channel-list">
          <div class="channel-item">
            <span class="channel-phase">Phase 1</span>
            <span>Direct-to-consumer — recreational boaters seeking sustainable, high-performance alternatives</span>
          </div>
          <div class="channel-item">
            <span class="channel-phase">Phase 2</span>
            <span>Boat manufacturers and shipyards integrating ABLTV into new vessel production</span>
          </div>
          <div class="channel-item">
            <span class="channel-phase">Phase 3</span>
            <span>Transport companies, commercial fleets, and maritime operators retrofitting existing vessels</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Exit Strategy / Growth Path -->
    <hr class="divider" />
    <section class="exit-section animate-in delay-3">
      <h2 class="section-title">Exit Strategy &amp; Growth Path</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">A phased global expansion plan designed for maximum market penetration and investor liquidity.</p>

      <div class="exit-timeline">
        <div class="exit-phase glass-box">
          <div class="exit-phase-header">
            <span class="exit-phase-badge seed-badge">Seed Phase</span>
            <span class="exit-phase-sub">Current</span>
          </div>
          <h3>Wefunder Crowdfunding</h3>
          <p>Open equity crowdfunding on Wefunder to raise initial startup capital, build community ownership, and validate product-market fit with early adopters.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="exit-phase glass-box">
          <div class="exit-phase-header">
            <span class="exit-phase-badge seriesa-badge">Series A</span>
            <span class="exit-phase-sub">Next Stage</span>
          </div>
          <h3>Commercial &amp; Government Expansion</h3>
          <p>Expansion into commercial fishing fleets, maritime enforcement agencies, and government contracts. Institutional capital enables scaled production and regulatory certification.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="exit-phase glass-box">
          <div class="exit-phase-header">
            <span class="exit-phase-badge global-badge">Global</span>
            <span class="exit-phase-sub">Rollout</span>
          </div>
          <h3>Regional Manufacturing Hubs</h3>
          <p>Franchise model for localized manufacturing: Central America/Caribbean → Mediterranean/Aegean → Nordics → SE Asia. Each hub serves regional demand with 3D-printable ABLTV units.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Profit Sharing -->
    <hr class="divider" />
    <section class="profit-section animate-in delay-3">
      <h2 class="section-title">Profit Sharing</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Profit with purpose — every venture fuels marine conservation.</p>

      <div class="glass-box profit-box">
        <div class="profit-icon">
          <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
            <path d="M8 12l2 2 4-4"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p class="profit-text">
          Fluidity Marine's for-profit ventures commit a <strong>substantial portion of profits</strong> 
          to fund <strong>Sinking Man Org</strong>'s non-profit marine conservation initiatives. 
          Every successful commercial deployment directly supports ocean cleanup, habitat restoration, 
          and marine ecosystem preservation — creating a self-sustaining cycle where market success 
          and environmental stewardship reinforce one another.
        </p>
        <p class="profit-text muted">
          This cross-venture profit commitment is built into our corporate DNA, ensuring that 
          as Fluidity Marine grows, so does its positive impact on the oceans we depend on.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="cta-portal animate-in delay-4">
      <div class="glass-box portal-box">
        <h2>Ready to Invest?</h2>
        <p>Review our formal disclosure and join the mission on Wefunder. Participate in the future of marine propulsion.</p>
        <div class="portal-actions">
          <a href="https://wefunder.com/fluidity" class="button button-primary button-lg" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            Invest on Wefunder
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* ─── Badge ─── */
  .badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;
    background: rgba(0, 242, 254, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 242, 254, 0.15);
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--cyan);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .badge-dot {
    width: 7px;
    height: 7px;
    background: var(--cyan);
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: pulse-glow 2s infinite;
  }

  /* ─── Stats Grid ─── */
  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .stat-card { padding: 1.5rem; text-align: center; }

  .stat-card-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .stat-card-value {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--cyan);
  }

  /* ─── Thesis Grid ─── */
  .thesis-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .thesis-card { padding: 2rem; }

  .thesis-icon {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: rgba(0, 242, 254, 0.08);
    color: var(--cyan);
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  .thesis-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }

  .thesis-card p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ─── Vision ─── */
  .vision-text {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 750px;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .vision-text strong { color: #fff; }

  .vision-stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .vision-stat { }

  .vision-stat-value {
    display: block;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--cyan);
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .vision-stat-label {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  /* ─── Timeline ─── */
  .milestone-timeline {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 2.5rem;
  }

  .milestone-timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 8px;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: var(--border);
  }

  .milestone {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .milestone:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .milestone-marker {
    position: absolute;
    left: -2.5rem;
    top: 4px;
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--bg);
    border: 2px solid var(--text-muted);
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .milestone.completed .milestone-marker {
    background: var(--cyan);
    border-color: var(--cyan);
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 242, 254, 0.3);
  }

  .milestone.active .milestone-marker {
    background: var(--cyan);
    border-color: var(--cyan);
    animation: pulse-glow 2s infinite;
  }

  .milestone-status {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .milestone.completed .milestone-status { color: var(--cyan); }
  .milestone.active .milestone-status { color: var(--cyan); }

  .milestone-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #fff;
    margin: 0 0 0.4rem;
  }

  .milestone-content p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ─── CTA Portal ─── */
  .cta-portal { margin-top: 5rem; }

  .portal-box {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem;
  }

  .portal-box h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: #fff;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .portal-box p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    max-width: 550px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .portal-actions {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  /* ─── Offering Details ─── */
  .offering-card {
    padding: 2.5rem;
  }

  .offering-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }

  .offering-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.2rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .offering-item:nth-last-child(-n+2) {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .offering-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .offering-value {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
  }

  /* ─── Use of Funds ─── */
  .funds-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .funds-card {
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .funds-card h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #fff;
    margin: 0 0 0.6rem;
  }

  .funds-card p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .funds-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .funds-bar {
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .bar-rd { background: var(--cyan); }
  .bar-mkt { background: #00e5a0; }
  .bar-ops { background: #7c6df0; }
  .bar-legal { background: #f0a36d; }
  .bar-wc { background: #f06d8a; }

  .funds-pct {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--cyan);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  /* ─── Market Size ─── */
  .market-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .market-stat {
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .market-stat-value {
    display: block;
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    font-weight: 900;
